    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;Dead Sale&quot;</strong> is an episodic horror game that features different stories. In each episode, players must find a way to escape various locations, mainly houses and properties that are up for sale. However, each of these places has been the site of disturbing, dark, and human events.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Main Mechanic:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a mysterious mirror to reveal what has been hidden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267050/extras/f17b6d7f48afc02b593a91a223f741c7.poster.avif?t=1743704813\" width=564 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267050/extras/f17b6d7f48afc02b593a91a223f741c7.webm?t=1743704813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267050/extras/f17b6d7f48afc02b593a91a223f741c7.mp4?t=1743704813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Atmosphere:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a unique aesthetic, with sepia tones that draw you into the dark depths of this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267050/extras/af4c40f13abc52b349c3681dccd9d0bb.poster.avif?t=1743704813\" width=564 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267050/extras/af4c40f13abc52b349c3681dccd9d0bb.webm?t=1743704813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267050/extras/af4c40f13abc52b349c3681dccd9d0bb.mp4?t=1743704813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dark Backstory:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a deeply disturbing story, uncover the origin of the terrifying events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267050/extras/1112d312465ae559d9d77a88d77c4f3d.poster.avif?t=1743704813\" width=564 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267050/extras/1112d312465ae559d9d77a88d77c4f3d.webm?t=1743704813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267050/extras/1112d312465ae559d9d77a88d77c4f3d.mp4?t=1743704813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple Endings:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover different ways to escape the house, though some may not be as lucky as others.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice acting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sepia tone aesthetic</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Photorealistic graphics</p></li></ul>",
